            <title>[LUCENE-2503] light/minimal stemming for euro languages</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2503</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;The snowball stemmers are very aggressive and it would be nice if there were lighter alternatives.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Some applications may want to perform less aggressive stemming, for example:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.lucidimagination.com/search/document/5d16391e21ca6faf/plural_only_stemmer&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot;&gt;http://www.lucidimagination.com/search/document/5d16391e21ca6faf/plural_only_stemmer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Good, relevance tested algorithms exist and I think we should provide these alternatives.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
